reviewText: A good review of the Lighthouses in Rhode Island

"Rhode Island's Historic Lighthouses" is the only program to include all 30 of Rhode Island's beacons past and present. Stunning aerial photography takes you over the coastline and past some of the oldest lighthouses in the nation. Listen to stories about tragic hurricanes and restoration from the people who were there. This Emmy nominated program has been seen on public television and is a good watch for lighthouse enthusiast and the casual viewer. You'll enjoy taking this journey over and over.
